MAXINE MILLER, as executrix of the Estate of Glennah T. Murphrey, deceased, et al., v. JOHN W. PARKER, et al. 15 So. (2nd) 419

June Term, 1943

October 22, 1943 Division A Rehearing Denied November 16, 1943 M. A. Rosin, for appellants. Hugh Gilbert Jones, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

The record and briefs have been duly considered and finding no error in the record the decree is affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
